```java
Stone stone; // 发射的石头
Stone targetStone; // 静止的目标小球
PollutionTarget pollution; // 污染目标
boolean isCharging = false;
float charge = 0;
float maxCharge = 100;
long chargeStartTime;

void setup() {
    size(800, 600);
    stone = new Stone(20, 50, height - 100, 0.3);
    targetStone = new Stone(20, width / 2, height - 50, 0.3);
    pollution = new PollutionTarget(width - 100, height - 50, 40);
}

void draw() {
    background(255);
    handleCharging();
    stone.update();
    stone.display();
    targetStone.display();
    pollution.display();

    if (stone.checkCollision(targetStone)) {
        calculateCollision();
    }

    if (targetStone.checkCollision(pollution)) {
        pollution.hit(); // 污染目标被清理
        targetStone.stop(); // 停止静止的石头运动
    }
}

void mousePressed() {
    if (!stone.isFired && !isCharging) { // 如果石头尚未发射并且没有在蓄力中
        isCharging = true;
        chargeStartTime = millis();
    }
}

void mouseReleased() {
    if (isCharging) {
        isCharging = false;
        float chargeTime = millis() - chargeStartTime;
        float power = map(chargeTime, 0, 1000, 0, maxCharge);
        float angle = atan2(mouseY - stone.y, mouseX - stone.x);
        stone.fire(power, angle);
    }
}

void handleCharging() {
    if (isCharging) {
        charge = map(millis() - chargeStartTime, 0, 1000, 0, maxCharge);
        charge = constrain(charge, 0, maxCharge);
    } else {
        charge = 0;
    }
    // 显示蓄力条
    fill(0, 255, 0);
    rect(25, height - 25, charge, 20);
}

void calculateCollision() {
    // 假定两个石头的质量相等
    float m = stone.size; // 使用石头的size代表质量

    // 假设完全弹性碰撞，按照动量守恒定律计算碰撞之后两个物体的速度
    PVector v1Initial = stone.velocity.copy();
    PVector v2Initial = targetStone.velocity.copy();

    // 这里我们可以简化计算，因为靶子石头是静止的
    PVector v1Final = new PVector((m - m) / (m + m) * v1Initial.x, v1Initial.y);
    PVector v2Final = new PVector((m + m) / (m + m) * v1Initial.x, v1Initial.y);

    stone.velocity = v1Final;
    targetStone.velocity = v2Final;
    stone.stop(); // 停止发射的石头运动

    // NOTE: 实际上这两个速度都是同一个速度值，因为二者质量相同，且碰撞前一个物体静止
}
```

在上述代码中，蓄力条的显示和处理逻辑被封装在 `handleCharging` 函数内，石头的发射逻辑在 `mouseReleased` 事件中处理。当发射的石头与静止的石头发生碰撞时，会调用 `calculateCollision` 函数，这个函数根据动量守恒定律计算两个石头的最终速度。

